title: ++Gifting Fairy's Halloween Costume GIVEAWAY++
body:
Hey everyone its me again!! Time for another gifting thread, it's been awhile. 

**This event will be running from Oct. 28 - Nov. 2, 7pm EST!!!**

Since it's my favorite time of the year I thought I'd be nice and do another giveaway.  The first 50 people that upload a picture of themselves in costume will be gifted a 975 Mystery Skin.  I will also be picking out 3 people to give a special prize for having the best costumes.

Gift Chart:

First 50 w/costume: One 975 Mystery Skin
1st Best Dressed: $100 RP
2nd Best Dressed: $50 RP
3rd Best Dressed: $25 RP


OK so, here is how it works.

**NOTE: USE IMGUR or another site to upload your pics.**  

1) **Write on a piece of paper "Gifting Fairy", this MUST be in the picture.**  This is just to ensure you aren't stealing someone else's pictures to get a gift.

2) Upload a picture of yourself dressed up for Halloween **with the paper** to this thread.  This costume can be bought or made, doesn't matter but it MUST be you. **And a real costume, not a blanket over your head.  This also goes for just wearing cat ears or a halo.  You need to be dressed up**. xD

3) Wait for me to add you to my friends list.** I have to wait 24 hours before I can send the gifts out and I can only send 10 gifts per day so be patient.** c;

I hope you guys enjoy this event and have fun this Halloween.  Also, I'll be late on gifting Saturday since it's Halloween.  I expect most people will be posting the picture the day of Halloween or after, but I wanted to give you guys a heads up! 

Oh and for anyone doubting if this is legit or not, here is a past post on my other event.  This is 100% legit.  If you have any questions feel free to ask.

http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/memes/qX8TAXgh-the-gifting-fairy-new-thread
